latestPosts.caption: wrote this last year in July when I was going through something, clearly, that I now can neither remember nor grasp the intensity of. and yet, all of it feels as though it could’ve been written a second ago - and maybe that’s what will keep me writing forever.

Photo by nona ☀️ on July 07, 2025. May be an image of text that says 'July July. Growing pains. Inability to move on. Inability to stand still. Making mistakes. Making amends. Promising won't repeat the mistakes. And repeat. Losing face. Admitting defeat. Feeling ashamed. Embracing shame. Tightening some ties. Ripping out others. Wondering. Wonderment. Want. Wandering. All sound the same. Wandered plenty. Lost my way. Living in questions. What if? Living in answers. What was. What is. What will never be. Why not? Just not. Sometimes happy.'.

Photo by nona ☀️ on July 07, 2025. May be an image of grass and text that says 'Sometimes sad. Sometimes wonder if that's the whole point. Only sent one text Regret. Lots. All the time. Forgiveness, regret. fleetingly. Then regret. Heartbroken. Just because it wasn't romantic doesn't mean its end wasn't tragic. Healed. Heartbroken again. What is still bothering you? Still. Stillness of time. Still stuck in time. Still stuck. But healed, somewhat, still. Still. Older. Certainly older Wiser, slightly. Stupid. So, so stupid. Still loved. Still adored. Not by all. Not by one. But most. Usually smiling. Only cried once. Consequence of being burned.'.

Photo by nona ☀️ on July 07, 2025. May be an image of grass and text that says 'Happier, unequivocally. Aware that life gets tougher. Life got tough. Aware that life is good, if not perfect. Life got bad. Living still. Living somehow. Aware that nothing, not even pain, not even life, lasts forever. Still gutted. Still heartbroken. But healed. Think about it sometimes. Think about it all night when I haven't thought about it all day. Heartbroken again. Sometimes happy. Sometimes angry. Sometimes forgiving. Sometimes vengeful. Always broken and healed and broken and healed and broken and healed and broken and healed and broken and healed and broken and healed. August.'.
